# Registering

AlexSol provides registering 4 types of users: Administrator user, consultant user, company owner user and employee user. And the admin user is also divided into: super and support admin.

---

- [Register as Consultant](#consultant)
- [Register as Company Owner](#company_owner)
- [Register as Employee](#employee)

<a name="consultant"></a>
## Register as Consultant

> {primary} There are different actions they can perform for different types of users. For example, while a staff member can open a ticket, he cannot change the deadline of that ticket. But a consultant or company owner can change it.


To register, click on the "Consultant Signup" button on the main page.
![screenshot](data:image/png;base64,)




To complete the registration, you must fill in the required information on the page that opens.
![screenshot](data:image/png;base64,)




<a name="company_owner"></a>
## Register as Company Owner

To register, click on the "Consultant Signup" button and after then "Register company" button on the main page.
![screenshot](data:image/png;base64,)




To complete the registration, you must fill in the required information on the page that opens.
![screenshot](data:image/png;base64,)
